          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can you resize my jewelry if it doesn’t fit?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<h5>Absolutely! I offer complimentary resizing for custom jewelry. However, some pieces, such as heavily engraved rings, eternity-style, or flush-set rings, may not be resizable. Please contact me to discuss your specific needs, and I’ll ensure your piece fits perfectly.</h5>",
